From 698133500942648e4574310868ec08258270bd77 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: =?UTF-8?q?Bartek=20Iwa=C5=84czuk?= <biwanczuk@gmail.com>
Date: Thu, 7 May 2026 15:58:09 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 1/2] perf(ext/node): convert more polyfills to lazy-loaded JS

Convert 6 node:* modules from eagerly-loaded ESM to lazy-loaded IIFE
scripts with thin ESM wrappers: node:os, node:string_decoder, node:test,
node:test/reporters, node:stream/consumers, node:stream/web.

Update import sites in 01_require.js, constants.ts, internal/tty.js,
internal/streams/readable.js, internal/crypto/cipher.ts,
internal/readline/emitKeypressEvents.mjs, internal/readline/interface.mjs,
and internal/webstreams/adapters.js to use core.loadExtScript() instead
of ESM imports.
---
